fields.label: Grid Item Image Link
fields.name: grid_item_image_link
fields.instructions: Take the grid item's link, and add it to the grid item's image/icon.

fields.label: Alternative Background Margin?
fields.name: alternative_background_margin
fields.instructions: Checking this will cause the background color to end where/cut through the middle of the top row of your icons.

sub_fields.label: Show Arrow Watermark?
sub_fields.name: show_arrow_watermark
sub_fields.instructions: This adds a slightly transparent arrow icon in the bottom right of your hero.

sub_fields.label: Background Darkness Overlay
sub_fields.name: background_darkness_overlay
sub_fields.instructions: Specify the opacity of the dark overlay on your slide. Minimum value: 30%.

fields.label: Copy
fields.name: copy
fields.instructions: Enter copy here, and it will show up within the background/container your icons live in, as opposed to directly above it in white.

fields.label: What would you like to display?
fields.name: what_to_show
